questions.quote: Oh my God! YOU FORGOT THE PIES? Well, I cannot believe this. You force me to make dinner, then you're an hour late and you forget the one little thing that I asked you to do.
Eww! No!! Her ear! All right, Monica categorizes her towels. How many categories are there?
I will find a selfless good deed! 'Cause I just gave birth to three children and I will not let them be raised in a world where Joey is right!
Hmm. Do you think-Could you tell me if she's hanging in, in a one bedroom or a two?
No Phoebe! I just need you there for support. I haven't told him I'm pregnant yet.
No, no, that-that, that's all right. Umm, I'm just glad you called.
Well, isn't that a good thing? You said you were sick of this.
Oh, uh, again. Can I make a special request: Can you bring everything as soon as it's ready? Appetizers, entrees, we don't care.
Yeah, but, ah, ah, nothing has to happen. We're just having fun. You know, not everything had to go as far as "eye-contact."
Okay, so I'm done my part, okay. It's your responsibility now, okay. The burden is off me, right?
